snippet.title: Coffee Crisis Gameplay PC / Switch Trailer - Mega Cat Studios Video Game
snippet.description:
Crush alien overlords with Metal-fueled, caffeine aided combos to save Earth’s most precious resources.  Feel their extra-terrestrial flesh rip to shreds and crank the alien cries to 11.

Get it on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/596380/Coffee_Crisis/

Join the conversation on Discord:  https://discord.gg/gwyUy6s
For more on Mega Cat Studios and our games, please visit: https://megacatstudios.com/

Come play & talk on discord! www.discord.gg/megacat
